{"title":"ES6语法笔记","date":"2019-10-17T01:18:56.000Z","link":"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记","tags":["前端","笔记"],"updated":"2019-11-02T06:57:32.000Z","content":"<h2 id=\"ES6语法笔记\">ES6语法笔记<a href=\"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记#ES6语法笔记\"></a></h2><p><img src=\"http://148.70.50.70/source/1571275129928.jpg\" alt=\"image.png\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"箭头函数\">箭头函数<a href=\"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记#箭头函数\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var f = a =&gt; a;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>等同于</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var f = function(a)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         return a;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>箭头左侧的是代表参数，若参数只有一个，()可以省略，箭头右侧的表示函数代码块，若代码块里面是个返回值，则{}可以省略不写。</p>\n<h4 id=\"无参数\">无参数<a href=\"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记#无参数\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var f = () =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    console.log(&quot;无参&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"有参数\">有参数<a href=\"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记#有参数\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> var f = (a, b) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       return a+b;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">var f = a =&gt; a;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"返回对象\">返回对象<a href=\"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记#返回对象\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var f = () =&gt; (&#123;name:&apos;David&apos;, age:23&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"注意点\">注意点<a href=\"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记#注意点\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var a = &apos;Global&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   var obj=&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       a:&apos;Local&apos;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       f1:function()&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           console.log(this.a);</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">       f2:()=&gt;&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           console.log(this.a);</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   obj.fn1();</span><br><span class=\"line\">   obj.fn2();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h6 id=\"输出\">输出<a href=\"2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记#输出\"></a></h6><p>Local<br>Global</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Springboot整合redis","link":"2019/10/17/Springboot整合redis"},"next":{"title":"web-app开发笔记","link":"2019/10/09/web-app开发笔记"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/10/17/ES6语法笔记/","toc":[{"title":"ES6语法笔记","id":"ES6语法笔记","index":"1","children":[{"title":"箭头函数","id":"箭头函数","index":"1.1","children":[{"title":"无参数","id":"无参数","index":"1.1.1"},{"title":"有参数","id":"有参数","index":"1.1.2"},{"title":"返回对象","id":"返回对象","index":"1.1.3"},{"title":"注意点","id":"注意点","index":"1.1.4"}]}]}]}